  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rusty Dudes is a game about managing a gang of mercenaries.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a level with different missions, mercenaries, and unique perks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test the strength of your gang on arena maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maneuver and use active abilities to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete bonus tasks or escape with what you have? It's up to you because you're the leader of the Rusty Dudes gang!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What are you waiting for? Go ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
